/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出面既花花世界<br />\n比較精彩<br />\n我已經留唔住佢<br />\n仲想攞埋我黎伏後備<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458bba319219383bfc6a96273421ae7b2f470457","tid":61250,"uid":15195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:23:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>分手後叫我等三年<br />\n咁點解仲要分手<br />\n三年後你返到黎<br />\n我都唔會同你係埋一齊<br />\n賤格<br />\n<br />\n利申 自言自語<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n話未準備好只係唔想同我一齊姐 但對住第個可以準備好架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出面既花花世界<br />\n比較精彩<br />\n我已經留唔住佢<br />\n仲想攞埋我黎<span style=\"color: red;\">做</span>後備<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e4cf51aaa8abba74e6a21dc652e3b314ea0b1ed6","tid":61250,"uid":8118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:24:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚似我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都是犯賤的<br />\n有啲啲野明知唔會發生 都硬係去等去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我不怕 死心不息愛你<br />\n表演討好的雜技<br />\n不惜更改性格都想配合你<br />\n施展魔鬼的嫵媚<br />\n加起修女莊嚴難以令你在意得到轉機<br />\n然後我 假裝瀟灑對你<br />\n偷歡偷不到妒忌<br />\n花心癡心竟然同樣不震撼你<br />\n哭泣表演可憐你嫌棄<br />\n大概正中你厭惡的禁忌<br />\n難道要我說我愛到想死<br />\n威脅若拒絕我便逼死你<br />\n又怕越快被你拋棄<br />\n<br />\n每次聽都好似講緊自己咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796224c0cb2e76752eec0c7c03b7c39fef05b750","tid":61250,"uid":8118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:24:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n騎牛揾馬 你就係牛 我身邊個女仔就係馬&hellip; sorry</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解你要同我講你有鐘意嘅人？係咪想我祝福你？定係會令我易啲放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想你知難而退&hellip; 點知你煩左我成年&hellip; 屌！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時係你搵我先架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11860d2412cba1020a096491e2390cdefe483426","tid":61250,"uid":8118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:25:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>分手後叫我等三年<br />\n咁點解仲要分手<br />\n三年後你返到黎<br />\n我都唔會同你係埋一齊<br />\n賤格<br />\n<br />\n利申 自言自語<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n話未準備好只係唔想同我一齊姐 但對住第個可以準備好架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出面既花花世界<br />\n比較精彩<br />\n我已經留唔住佢<br />\n仲想攞埋我黎伏後備<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我連後備都唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5025a6b3dbb23f4733b6b39315621152b2baca0b","tid":61250,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:26:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買左啲野俾佢 以為得佢一個等緊我 點知佢隔離有個女仔同佢一齊等<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我bye bye都無講 俾完佢就走左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉身必須比眼淚更早 可惜你未知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2016就咁算啦 2017唔好見啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n恭喜晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b95a684a8552e87f6531d577ce89ed0d39c4fa5","tid":61250,"uid":8118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-